act.article:
1 Short title and commencement.—
i These rules may be called the National Tax Tribunal (Salary, Allowances and other Conditions of Service of the Officers and Exployees) Rules, 2005;
ii They shall come into force on the date2 of their publication in the Official Gazette.

2 Definitions.—In 
these rules, unless the context otherwise requires,


       
a  “employees” means the employees of the Tribunal;


       
b  “officers” means the officer of the Tribunal;


       
c  “Tribunal” means the National Tax Tribunal established under section 3 
of the National Tax Tribunal Act, 2005.
